{"title":"Crust Bikes Geared Wombat in Teal Sparkle","link":"https://theradavist.com/crust-bikes-geared-wombat-teal/","date":1720710000000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Crust_Bikes_Geared_Wombat_2024.jpeg?fit=1200,1365&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Crust_Bikes_Geared_Wombat_2024.jpeg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Crust_Bikes_Geared_Wombat_2024.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Crust_Bikes_Geared_Wombat_2024.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Crust_Bikes_Geared_Wombat_2024.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/Crust_Bikes_Geared_Wombat_2024.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/?s=Crust+Bike\" target=\"_blank\">Crust Bike</a>‘s <a href=\"https://crustbikes.com/products/geared-wombat?variant=46468871192887\" target=\"_blank\">Geared Wombat</a>, the modern 27.5″ wheeled rigid MTB, got a new coat of paint for 2024…<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3503.jpg?fit=1200,1365&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3503.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3503.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3503.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3503.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3503.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3505.jpg?fit=1200,1365&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3505.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3505.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3505.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3505.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/FP_3505.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Now in a Teal Sparkle paint job, featuring a teal undercoat with dark green and white speckles and bright orange decals. These Wombat frames are designed to clear 27.5 x 2.6″ tires, so if you want to ride chonk, it’s got clearance for that or if you want a more mixed terrain setup, roll a 2.3″ tire. For the long haul, there are rack and cargo cage mounts. Run v-brakes or cantilevers, and if you would like to get rowdy, there’s dropping routing for that.</p>\n<p>Check out the new color Wombat at <a href=\"https://crustbikes.com/products/geared-wombat?variant=46468871192887\" target=\"_blank\">Crust Bikes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/crust-bikes-geared-wombat-teal/\">Crust Bikes Geared Wombat in Teal Sparkle</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"6206eea5aca1a628567e103222fa3dc712d597f7f1b68cb2d50e4a3539d48b16","category":"Cycling"}